@startuml
title LowCortisol WebApp - IAM Frontend Bounded Context Layers
left to right direction
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0
hide circle

package "IAM Frontend Bounded Context" {
  class "Domain" as Frontend_iam_Domain <<layer>>
  class "Application" as Frontend_iam_Application <<layer>>
  class "Infrastructure" as Frontend_iam_Infrastructure <<layer>>
  class "Presentation" as Frontend_iam_Presentation <<layer>>
}

Frontend_iam_Presentation ..> Frontend_iam_Application : user actions / state
Frontend_iam_Application ..> Frontend_iam_Domain : models and rules
Frontend_iam_Application ..> Frontend_iam_Infrastructure : API services / adapters
Frontend_iam_Infrastructure ..> Frontend_iam_Domain : resources and mappers
Frontend_iam_Presentation ..> Frontend_iam_Domain : view models

note bottom of Frontend_iam_Application
Detailed class diagrams for each layer are available in docs/diagrams/class/frontend/layers/iam.
end note

@enduml
